	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ahhh... at level 25, it's kinda hard to scrap out 100 plat.&nbsp;&nbsp;250 is like a dream.<br><br>Anyways if you want the mogguk and have no money for it.  Powerlevel an Enchanter up to 12.  If you have friends who are in their 20's, it's only a 6 to 8 hour process to get to 12.  Then use that Chanter to get the Moggok.<br><br>You'll only need 30 plats or less to get the appropriate enchanter spells to complete the quest at level 12. Figure out the rest and good luck.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
