	   <tr><td colspan=2>i have just started a Wizard on the Tarew Marr server and it is my first time as a caster: let me say this after playing a Warrior to lvl 32 a Ranger to 18 and a Monk to 20 the Wizard (16 now) is the most fun i have had. Now there is a need for all types of classes in a group i mean without the tank the casters die without healers the tanks die and the casters smooth all the rough edges out. Now my wizard is Twinked a bit but i had to work so hard on my warrior that i feel i deserve it(178INT and have 8 slots open) but i am hoping to get ports soon for my guild so we can do more stuff together. if you ever need a port on Tarew Marr and i am not busy just yell.<br><br>Tela (Wizard for Death Before Dishonor) Tarew Marr server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
