	   <tr><td colspan=2>To all those that say Wizards are nerfed your totally wrong. Just look at the new spells there giving us (tranlocate). I have played a wiz for a long time and at lower lvls they are hard to play you just have to get into good groups a Wiz is not the soloer and if you don't nuke hard you won't die as much. AOE spells usually spell death unless you have a really good group. I know it seems like you are not pulling your weight if your not doing constant damage like warriors are but if you nuke about half way thru then nuke when the mob turns and runs the group will appreciate it since they don't have to chase the mob down. When you do finally get to the higher lvls you will be indipensible since you are the only one who can take people to planes nuke for 250 in secs and evac the group when things start going wrong and save everyones life. I just did this the other night and as a WIZ you feel a great deal of accomplishment. Mana control is biggest thing and as you lvl you should start to see this.<br><br>Nevaro Ravenspawn<br>Wizard of 34th season<br>Drinal<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
