	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sorry... EE is not a groupers delite. You bring a friend or a couple of friends along with you and he'll use your DD on your friends.<br><br>Solo it with your Wiz at 24.&nbsp;&nbsp;Blast EE from afar.  Root pet aside, and continue blasting.  He'll go down fast with Frost Shock.  Have good magic resistance gear on.  He would usually cast Tash on you to open, but if Frost shock hits for full each time, Tash will be the only spell he'll be able to cast.<br><br>I guess you can take a friend along to take care of any muddites or minos that wanna join in.  Just tell them to stay away from EE's agro range so incase he charms you, they'll be safe.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
