	   <tr><td colspan=2>Cancel Magic removes charm, but Murphy's Law dictates that it will only uncharm them after you have removed all their buffs first.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>If someone in the group gets charmed Root, Snare or fear them if you don't have cancel magic.  To avoid Charm, use your magic resist buffs and have them put on any magic resist gear they have (magic resist is more important that AC when fighting EE's).  <br><br>Another tactic is to try to keep the eye stunned or feared so it can't cast at all.<br><br>Good Luck<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
