	   <tr><td colspan=2>I also started out with an Erudite Wiz. Tox is not friendly but it can sustain you to level 8.&nbsp;&nbsp;The best place for any newbie non-evil race to go to is Misty Thicket.  It has to be the safest place to level and it has mobs that can take you all the way to level 12.  The guards have a pretty good attack radius for mobs.  Only bad thing about that is if you fight too close to the deputies, they will steal your kill.  But it's ok.  They'll save you more than they will kill steal from you.  It's a pain to get there though if you are coming from Erud, but it's all worth it.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
